What you'll be doing
Manage and oversee the engineering development process for new products;
Collaborate with cross-functional teams to design and develop innovative solutions;
Ensure compliance with industry regulations and internal quality standards;
Analyse product performance data and implement continuous improvement initiatives;
Mentor and provide guidance to junior engineers within the team;
Act as a technical subject matter expert and support the broader organisation;
What we're looking for
Degree in Mechanical Engineering or a related field;
Minimum 5 years' experience in a product development or engineering supervision role;
Proven track record of managing complex engineering projects from concept to completion;
Excellent problem-solving, analytical and decision-making skills;
Strong project management and stakeholder management abilities;
Proficient in the use of Core Tools IATF 16949;2016;
Effective communication and interpersonal skills to work across teams;
About us
PT Abimanyu Sekar Nusantara' is a leading manufacturer of high-quality industrial products in Indonesia. With a focus on innovation and sustainability, we are committed to delivering cutting-edge engineering solutions to our customers. Our team of dedicated professionals are passionate about their work and strive to exceed expectations every day.
If you're ready to take the next step in your career and join a dynamic, forward-thinking organisation, we encourage you to apply for this role.
